## Snippet
SPDXID: SDOC-JAZZ-INTEGRATION
name: Requirement 'Jazz integration'
summary: SPDX Snippet for requirement SDOC-JAZZ-INTEGRATION
description: The StrictDoc OSLC RM server shall interoperate with Jazz as an OSLC RM 2.0 provider.
comment: This snippet has been generated from a requirement defined in a StrictDoc file: hello.sdoc.
