## Snippet
SPDXID: SDOC-JAZZ-ROOT-SERVICES
name: Requirement 'Root services discovery'
summary: SPDX Snippet for requirement SDOC-JAZZ-ROOT-SERVICES
description: The server shall publish an RDF/XML OSLC root-services document that advertises the RM service-provider catalog and Jazz OSLC catalog descriptor.
comment: This snippet has been generated from a requirement defined in a StrictDoc file: hello.sdoc.
