## Snippet
SPDXID: SDOC-JAZZ-SERVICE-PROVIDER
name: Requirement 'Service provider catalog'
summary: SPDX Snippet for requirement SDOC-JAZZ-SERVICE-PROVIDER
description: The server shall expose an RM service-provider catalog that lists the StrictDoc document service providers and their RM domain.
comment: This snippet has been generated from a requirement defined in a StrictDoc file: hello.sdoc.
