## Snippet
SPDXID: SDOC-JAZZ-INSTANCE-SHAPE
name: Requirement 'Requirement instance shape'
summary: SPDX Snippet for requirement SDOC-JAZZ-INSTANCE-SHAPE
description: Each requirement representation shall advertise a provider-owned OSLC RM instance shape that describes its writable link properties.
