## Snippet
SPDXID: SDOC-JAZZ-QUERY-SHAPE
name: Requirement 'Query capability resource shape'
summary: SPDX Snippet for requirement SDOC-JAZZ-QUERY-SHAPE
description: The RM query capability shall advertise the same requirement resource shape that individual requirement representations use.
